Powerful Suction

Strong suction is what outstands this product, ensuring the great cleaning performances on your various cleaning tasks.

5 Height Adjustment Settings

Just turn the dial to clean low to medium pile carpet, plush, high pile rugs, shag rug and hardfloors.

Intuitive assembly

Assembling this bagless upright vacuum cleaner is a breeze. Simply snap on the quick release handle, fix the hose, wrap the cord on.

For above floor cleaning simply attach the quick release handle to the stretch hose and pop on a vacuum tool attachment.

Tool Set

Product description

We want cleaning to suck less for you. The Eureka power speed all floor vacuum with attachments lets you give your house the clean it deserves without breaking your budget. Packed full of features like an XL dust cup, washable filter, accessories, and a wide nozzle, this lightweight but powerful vacuum cleaner won’t disappoint. Clean your floors and above with ease. It works on carpets, rugs, hardwood floors, cars, ceilings, lampshades, furniture, and more. Customer service: if you have any questions, please kindly contact our customer service team at customer service team at 1-800-282-2886.

I had to get a longer nozzel to do the floors nd because of the price, they do not include a longer nozzle, so when their telescopic nozzle is sold by Amazon this summer, will have to see the cost for it. The other problem with this vacuum is that when you pull out the top handle to clip the noxzzle to use for floors, walls etc the machine does fall down due to the lightness. This one is so much better. For the price it isnt perfect, but I like the reviews. The suction is great and cleans up my rugs full of dog hair.

August 28th, 2018 Still love this vacuum cleaner. I love that it is light weight, and how good it cleans my rugs and the floors. Customer service is pretty good too. The only thing is that I am not happy with the price of the foam filter. They last a couple of months if you keep clean. Amazon has it at $15.99. I did call Eureka, and they are sending me one at no cost, which I appreciate. For the cost of this vacuum, the filters should be competitive with other foam filters. By watching youtube, the air speed eureka vacuums have the same design canisters like the power speed, so I order a pack of eureka foam filters for the air speed to see if they would work the same. They cost over $8 dollars for 6. I will receive them this week and will try them. If they fit and work I will continue to buy them. I will update.

Will have to wait and see how long it last. I hope it works for a long time, I really like it.

September 1, 2018 The DCF-26 filters pack of 6, for the eureka airspeed fits the power speed vacuum that I have. It will be thicker, but it fits great. I ordered another 6 pack, cause the price is right. These are all just foam filters for Eureka vacuums, the power speed filter is too high.
Update:
Feb 13, 2019 Vacuum cleaner still strong and and wonderful to use. So easy still to clean, and does not hurt my back. I bought a second one for the upstairs rooms. Its worth every penny. It does a great job still, and so easy to clean.
June 2019 Still works great, I love this vacuum so light to move around. I work it out a lot, and it hasnt fail me. Now I have 2. One for the 2nd floor. It feels great to use and doesnt hurt my hands or my back, easy to attach the other brushes. Light enough to pickup.
